                  The world  can be heavy,  chaotic, complicated and yet
                  painstakingly boring.  At times, life feels so serious and it can
                  be difficult to remind ourselves to appreciate the simple
                  beauty that surrounds us. I hope these little practices add a
                  touch of silly whimsy to your inner landscape.
                  
                  Give a name to every squirrel you see today. Maybe one inspires you to create a backstory…
                  Research the first birdsong you hear when you wake up.  Learn all the cool facts about that bird and share with your friends or coworkers!
                  Whisper a wish into your morning tea/coffee/beverage before taking a sip. Consider it true."
